]] Coach of the Year.|ref=<ref name=\"Significant Sig\" />}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Jay Wright (coach)|Jay Wright]]|chapter= [[Bucknell University|Bucknell]], 1983|nota=Men's Basketball [[Coach (sports)|Coach]], [[Villanova University]], [[Big East Conference (1979\u20132013)|Big East]] Coach of the Year: 2006, 2009, 2014|ref=}}\n}}\n\n===Football===\n{{Mem/fstart\n|ilist = \n[[File:Bob Griese with soldier CROP.jpg|thumb|100px|Bob Griese]]\n<!-- Deleted image removed: [[File:Woody Hayes.jpg|thumb|100px|Woody Hayes]] -->\n[[File:Mike Holmgren 2004.jpg|thumb|100px|Mike Holmgren]]\n[[File:JohnnyMajorsPitt2009.jpg|thumb|100px|Johnny Majors]]\n<!-- [[WP:NFCC]] violation: [[File:Merlin Olsen.jpg|thumb|100px|Merlin Olsen]] -->\n<!-- [[WP:NFCC]] violation: [[File:John Pont.gif|thumb|100px|John Pont]] -->\n[[File:Clark Shaughnessy.jpg|thumb|100px|Clark Shaughnessy]]\n|alist=\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Fred Akers]]|chapter= [[University of Arkansas]] 1959 Running back, [[Purdue University]],1987\u201390|nota= Head Coach  [[University of Texas]], 1977\u201386. Head Coach [[University of Wyoming]] 1975\u201376. Head Coach|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Bud Adams|Kenneth \"Bud\" Adams]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter= [[University of Kansas]], 1944|nota= Owner of [[Tennessee Titans]].|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Bill Arnsparger]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter= [[Miami University|Miami]], 1950|nota=  [[New York Giants]] head coach, [[Miami Dolphins]] defensive coordinator, [[LSU Tigers football|LSU Tigers]] head coach, [[University of Florida]] athletic director, [[San Diego Chargers]] defensive coordinator.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Red Badgro]]|chapter= [[University of Southern California]]|nota= [[End (American football)|End]], [[National Football League|NFL]] [[New York Yankees (NFL)|New York Yankees]], 1927\u20131928, [[New York Giants]], 1930\u20131935, and [[Brooklyn Dodgers (NFL)|Brooklyn Dodgers]], 1936.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Matt Baker (football player)|Matthew Baker]]|chapter= [[University of North Carolina at Chape