istrict Attorney]], 1972\u20131984.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Michael J. Bryant|Michael Bryant]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter= [[University of British Columbia]], 1987|nota= Attorney General of Ontario 2003\u20132007, MPP.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Randy Crane]]|chapter= [[University of Texas]], 1985|nota= Youngest ever [[United States District Judge]] for the [[Southern District of Texas]] 2002-Present.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Jose Alejandro Gonzalez, Jr.]]|chapter= [[University of Florida]], 1952|nota= [[Justice]], [[United States District Court for the Southern District of Florida]] 1978-1996.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Mark Herring]]|chapter= [[University of Virginia]], 1983|nota= [[Attorney General of Virginia]], 2014\u2013present.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Wayne L. Kidwell|Wayne Kidwell]]|chapter= [[University of Idaho]], 1960|nota= Justice, [[Idaho Supreme Court]], 1999\u20132005, [[Idaho Attorney General|Attorney General of Idaho]] 1975\u20131979.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[J. Michael Luttig]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter= [[Washington and Lee University]], 1976|nota= Former Federal Judge on the [[United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit]], 1991\u20132006.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Frank Murphy]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter= [[University of Michigan|Michigan]], 1912|nota= [[United States Attorney General]], 1939\u20131940; [[Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States]], 1940\u20131949.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Hardy Myers]]|chapter= [[University of Mississippi]], 1961|nota= [[Oregon Attorney General|Attorney General of Oregon]], 1996\u20132008.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[William C. O'Kelley|William O'Kelley]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter= [[Emory University]], 1951|nota= Senior Judge, [[United States District Court]] 1970\u2013present.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Matthew G. Olsen|Matthew Olsen]]<small></small>|chapter= [[University of Virginia]], 1984|nota= American prosecutor and Director of the [[National Counterterrorism Center]] (NCTC), 2011\u20132014.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name= [[Jame