d]]|chapter=[[University of Utah]], 1947|nota=[[Quorum of the Twelve]], [[The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints]]|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Theodore M. Burton]]|chapter=[[University of Utah]], 1932|nota=[[First Quorum of Seventy]], [[The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints]]|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Terence Finlay]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter=[[University of Western Ontario]], 1959|nota=Retired [[Archbishop]] of the [[Anglican Church of Canada]]|ref=<ref name=\"Significant Sig\" />}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Titus Lowe]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter=[[Ohio Wesleyan]], 1900|nota=Bishop, [[Methodist Episcopal Church]] and [[The Methodist Church (USA)|The Methodist Church]]|ref=<ref name=\"Significant Sig\" />}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Arthur Wheelock Moulton]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter=[[Hobart and William Smith Colleges|Hobart College]], 1939|nota=Bishop and President of the [[Province 8 of the Episcopal Church in the United States of America|Pacific Province]] for the [[Episcopal Church in the United States of America|Episcopal Church]].|ref=<ref name=\"Significant Sig\" />}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[William B. Oden]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter=[[Oklahoma State University]], 1957|nota=Bishop, [[United Methodist Church]]|ref=<ref name=\"Significant Sig\" />}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Hugh W. Pinnock]]|chapter=[[University of Utah]], 1958|nota=First [[Quorum (Latter Day Saints)|Quorum]] of the [[Seventy (LDS Church)|Seventy]] and [[Presidency of the Seventy]] in [[The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints]]|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[William McFerrin Stowe]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter=[[University of Miami]], 1938|nota=Bishop, [[The Methodist Church (USA)|The Methodist Church]]|ref=<ref name=\"Significant Sig\" />}}\n}}\n\n== Notes ==\n''<small><sup>S</sup>- Has been awarded the Significant Sig Award</small>''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www2.sigmachi.org/foundation/significant_sigs.phtml|title=Sigma Chi List of Significant Sigs|publisher=|access-date=2007-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070625203531/http://w