uck]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter=[[University of Arkansas]], 1926|nota=[[Radio comedy]], ''[[Lum and Abner]]''.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[David Letterman]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter=[[Ball State University]], 1969|nota=Television personality, host, ''[[The Late Show with David Letterman]]''.|ref=<ref name=\"Famous\"/>}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Peter Lupus]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter=[[Butler University]], 1954|nota=Television actor, ''[[Mission: Impossible (1966 TV series)|Mission: Impossible]]''.|ref=}}\n\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Neal McDonough]]|chapter=[[Syracuse University]], 1988, Film Actor, ''[[88 Minutes]]'', ''[[The Guardian (2006 film)|The Guardian]]''|nota=|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Ted McGinley]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter=[[University of Southern California]], 1981|nota=Film & television actor, ''[[Married... with Children]]'', ''[[Hope & Faith]]''|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Burr McIntosh]]<sup>S</sup>|chapter=[[Lafayette College|Lafayette]], 1884, [[silent film]] actor, [[supporting actor]]|nota=|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Patrick Muldoon]]|chapter=[[University of Southern California]], 1991|nota=Actor, ''[[Melrose Place]]'', ''[[Starship Troopers (film)|Starship Troopers]]''.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Brett Murphy]]|chapter=[[University of Pittsburgh|Pittsburgh]], 2014|nota=actor, ''[[Fever Pitch]]'', ''[[Hope & Faith]]'', ''[[Damages (TV series)|Damages]]'', ''[[Saturday Night Live]]''.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Lee Norris]]|chapter=[[Wake Forest University]], 2004 Actor, ''[[One Tree Hill (TV series)|One Tree Hill]]''|nota=|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Fred Newman (actor)|Fred Newman]]|chapter=[[University of Georgia|Georgia]], 1974|nota=Actor, voice actor and composer. ''[[Men in Black (1997 film)|Men in Black]], ''[[Harry and the Hendersons]]'', ''[[Gremlins]]'', ''[[Grand Theft Auto 2]]''|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Brad Pitt]]|chapter=[[University of Missouri]], 1986|nota=Actor, ''[[Fight Club]]''.|ref=}}\n{{Mem/f|name=[[Ben Savage]]|chapter=[[Stanford University]], 2004|nota=Television actor, ''[[Boy Meets World]]''.