oire-Atlantique]],<ref name=\":24\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ouest-france.fr/pays-de-la-loire/nantes-44000/coronavirus-la-patiente-prise-en-charge-au-chu-de-nantes-est-une-medecin-en-vacances-a-la-baule-8a524926-5a18-11ea-b880-542ae49135b4|title=Coronavirus. La patiente prise en charge au CHU de Nantes est une m\u00e9decin en vacances \u00e0 La Baule|date=28 February 2020|website=Ouest-France|language=fr|access-date=27 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200228143440/https://www.ouest-france.fr/pays-de-la-loire/nantes-44000/coronavirus-la-patiente-prise-en-charge-au-chu-de-nantes-est-une-medecin-en-vacances-a-la-baule-8a524926-5a18-11ea-b880-542ae49135b4|archive-date=28 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> [[Ain]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ledauphine.com/edition-genevois-chablais-bellegarde-pays-de-gex/2020/02/29/un-deuxieme-cas-de-coronavirus-dans-le-pays-de-gex|title=Ain. Un deuxi\u00e8me cas de coronavirus dans le Pays de Gex|website=ledauphine.com|language=fr|access-date=29 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229113048/https://www.ledauphine.com/edition-genevois-chablais-bellegarde-pays-de-gex/2020/02/29/un-deuxieme-cas-de-coronavirus-dans-le-pays-de-gex|archive-date=29 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> [[Landes (department)|Landes]],<ref name=\"auto2\" /> [[Charente-Maritime]],<ref name=\":26\">{{cite web|url=https://www.lci.fr/sante/en-direct-coronavirus-trois-personnels-de-sante-de-l-hopital-tenon-contamines-2143314.html|title=EN DIRECT \u2013 Coronavirus : trois personnels de sant\u00e9 de l'h\u00f4pital Tenon contamin\u00e9s|website=LCI|language=fr|access-date=29 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229112053/https://www.lci.fr/sante/en-direct-coronavirus-trois-personnels-de-sante-de-l-hopital-tenon-contamines-2143314.html|archive-date=29 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> [[Mayenne]],<ref name=\":25\" /><ref name=\":25\" /> [[Ille-et-Vilaine]],<ref name=\":29\">{{cite web|url=